zim-tools
------------------------------------------
Various ZIM command line tools.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.5.4-1
  file-5.44-1
  libdocopt0-0.6.3-1bl1
  libgcc1-12.4.0-3
  libgumbo1-0.10.1-1bl2
  libicu74-74.2-1
  libstdc++6-12.4.0-3
  libzim9-9.2.3-1bl1
  zlib0-1.3.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  Mustache-4.1-1bl1
  binutils-2.43.1-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  libdocopt-devel-0.6.3-1bl1
  libgtest-devel-1.15.2-1bl1
  libgumbo-devel-0.10.1-1bl2
  libzim-devel-9.2.3-1bl1
  meson-1.3.2-1
  ninja-1.12.0-1
  zlib-devel-1.3.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/openzim/zim-tools

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/openzim/zim-tools/archive/refs/tags/3.5.0.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack zim-tools-3.5.0-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./zim-tools-3.5.0-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/zim-tools-3.5.0-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/zim-tools-3.5.0-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(zim-tools)
  /usr/bin/zimbench.exe
  /usr/bin/zimcheck.exe
  /usr/bin/zimdiff.exe
  /usr/bin/zimdump.exe
  /usr/bin/zimpatch.exe
  /usr/bin/zimrecreate.exe
  /usr/bin/zimsearch.exe
  /usr/bin/zimsplit.exe
  /usr/bin/zimwriterfs.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/zim-tools.README
  /usr/share/doc/zim-tools/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/zim-tools/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/zim-tools/README.md

